<div class="row justify-content-center my-5">
  <div class="col col-md-8 col-lg-6">
    <div class="card border-danger">
      <div class="card-header bg-danger text-white text-center">
        <h3 class="mb-0">⚠️ 오류가 발생했습니다</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body p-4">
        <h4 class="text-danger mb-2">에러 메시지: <%= message %></h4>
        <h5 class="text-muted mb-4">상태 코드: <%= error.status %></h5>
        
        <hr>
        
        <p class="text-secondary mb-3" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
          <strong>시스템 관리자:</strong> 박영환
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-muted small mb-1">정밀 에러 로그 (Stack Trace):</p>
        <div class="bg-light p-3 border rounded" style="max-height: 200px; overflow-y: auto;">
          <pre class="mb-0" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #555;"><%= error.stack %></pre>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center mt-4">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary me-2">홈으로 이동</a>
          <button onclick="history.back();" class="btn btn-primary">이전 화면</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>